OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day and cloudy at first.
OL,6,FThrough the course of the day cloud
OL,7,Fwill break up allowing increasingly
OL,8,Flong sunny spells to develop, with
OL,9,Fmostly clear skies by the end of the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Light winds and feeling
OL,11,Fwarm.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will be a dry night with
OL,14,Flargely clear skies, which will give
OL,15,Flate sunshine in the evening.
OL,16,FOvernight, a few mist and fog patches
OL,17,Fmay form inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
