OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAny isolated mist and fog
OL,6,Fpatches will be quick clear leaving a
OL,7,Fdry day with light winds and
OL,8,Fpredominantly clear skies giving
OL,9,Fplenty of sunshine. Feeling warm in
OL,10,Fthe sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,13,Fsettled and warm Thursday and Friday
OL,14,Fwith variable cloud and plenty of
OL,15,Fsunny spells. A mostly cloudy day on
OL,16,FSaturday with showers possible.
OL,17,FBreezier on Thursday, otherwise light
OL,18,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
